description: APEC-OMV has complex proteomics. In order to screen the key virulence factors of APEC-OMV, comparative proteomics between APEC-OMV isolated from APEC and APEC-OMV isolated from APEC infection with cells was carried out, laying a good foundation for the study of the pathogenicity and pathogenic mechanism of APEC-OMV
